    "description": "Tameny Inc. provides marriage information services in Japan. The company operates in three segments: Matchmaking Business; Casual Wedding Business; and Regional Revitalization/Q0L Business. It engages in the operation of marriage consultation offices and planning, development, and operation of matchmaking parties; planning, development, and operation of online matchmaking services, as well as member introduction platforms between matchmaking businesses, etc.; and production of casual wedding ceremonies and receptions, small weddings, wedding ceremony unveiling parties, photo weddings, wedding after-parties, etc. The company is also involved in the provision of matchmaking support systems, operation of matchmaking support centers, hosting of various events and seminars, etc. Further, it offers life, non-life, and wedding insurance to customers who use casual wedding service. The company was formerly known as Partner Agent, Inc. and changed its name to Tameny Inc. in September 2020. Tameny Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Shinagawa, Japan."
